➜台湾夫妻定居上海20年，买一套房专门喝茶：中国文化的根在这里
http://www.sohu.com/a/411390840_157906	24302
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=208118566&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200804/add4629cd9a64e2baa83316215758ce7.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>周光明和朱彤云是室内设计圈，</p>
<p>一对有名的设计师夫妇，</p>
<p>两人在上海一起工作、生活了十多年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200804/384e3d139b0e4e9180eceb8c19a0dc04.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200804/309b8909818c4741b24fb94020771a6c.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
